- Arqchitecture
    Scripting Layer (Pyplot)
        - its the matplot.pyplot part and is lighter than the artist layer

    Artist Layer(Artist)
        - Know how to put ink on the canvas
        - Artists
            - primitive: Line2D, Rectangles
            - composite: Axes, Figures

    Backend Layer (FigureCanvas, Renderer, Event)
        - Figure canvas: define and encompasses the area on witch figure is drawn
        - Renderer: how to draw a figure
        - Event: use keyboard and mouse clicks


Recommended read: http://www.aosabook.org/en/matplotlib.html